{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "普鲁托 冥途之梦 前篇",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "冥途之梦 前篇",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人的生命何其脆弱\\n而又短暂。\\n故人类是需要保护的弱者。\\n\\n即使是王也不例外。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "那大概是第一次见到王的时候。\\n王为与魔神战斗而寻找着契约龙，\\n来到了吾处。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人类的力量终究有限。\\n当时吾拒绝王，\\n让他珍惜那短暂的生命。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "但是王并未放弃他的战斗。\\n而后……\\n被魔神贯穿胸膛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_sty_bg_0092_100"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "早就给过你忠告了……\\n人类是多么弱小、可悲的生物。\\n\\n当吾决定至少要完成\\n这个男人的遗愿时……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“还没结束……\\n还没……我得继续战斗……”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "那是可悲却坚定的话语。\\n吾不禁问他：\\n“你不怕死亡吗？”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“死有什么好怕的？”\\n王笑着答道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“在你们看来，人的生命非常短暂吧。\\n不过……正因为\\n人们明白人生苦短，\\n所以才能奋发图强。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“转瞬即逝的时间……\\n人们在有限的时间里从过去继承希望，\\n并将其托付给未来。\\n只要能达成这个使命……\\n献出自己的生命也在所不惜！”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "啊啊，看来吾有天大的误解。\\n没有舍弃希望与斗志、\\n为了未来挣扎奋斗之人，\\n怎么能称其弱小。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这就是人类的强大之处；\\n这就是人类生命的光辉。\\n\\n如此美丽的光辉，\\n前所未见。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "龙的生命悠久漫长。\\n因此龙会在\\n岁月的长河中随波逐流。\\n\\n与生命的光辉无缘。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这个人类为了未来\\n而拼命抗争。\\n那作为龙……\\n吾又是为什么而活？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "与这个男人一起的话能找到答案吗？\\n与这位王一起的话\\n能让漫长得无趣的生命焕发光彩吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "吾不想令这难能可贵的光辉\\n消失殆尽。\\n\\n正因如此……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "王啊，与吾缔结契约吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_200010_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "与吾缔结契约后，\\n王捡回了一条命。\\n吾选择了与王\\n共同战斗到底。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "其后，在命运之日\\n与王一同死去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_sty_bg_0092_100"
        }
    ]
}